strings.Value: "Guy Shaseur De Lombair was a woodsman not unlike you. However, he favored dual elven curve blades instead of the bow. Beloq-Nur was his fellow Archknight, and he was an expert marksmen. It is said that he could shoot the wings off a stirge at a hundred meters..."
"Minotaur shit... Even if he was that good with a bow, why not just kill the stirge?"
